        <head>Related Material</head>
        <p>The Bentley Library also has related collections documenting the activities performed by the university secretary. These include (but are not limited to) the personal papers of Shirley Wheeler Smith and John C. Christensen, the records of the business office of the university (cataloged as University of Michigan. Financial Operations), and the papers of individual U-M presidents who worked in close partnership with Smith and Christensen. In addition, for information about similar topics in period following Smith's retirement, the researcher should consult the records of various vice presidents and of the Office of Assistant to the President and Secretary of the University.</p>
